room_title: Escape room "Guardians of Time" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
room_description: You are a keeper of time and space and it is your duty to ensure that all remains true. Unfortunately, one of your fellow keepers has forsaken the cause and has gone rogue through time causing chaos and creating a ripple in time that will destroy civilization. Gather as many timekeepers as you can and go back to the past to mend history before all is lost!
